<subSubSection pageId="3" pageNumber="4" type="remarks">
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
<bibRefCitation pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Borradaile (1902)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName class="Malacostraca" family="Portunidae" genus="Thalamita" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Thalamita exetastica" order="Decapoda" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="exetastica" subSpecies="macrodonta">Thalamita exetastica macrodonta</taxonomicName>
from two specimens from two islands in the Maldives, Kolumadulu and Suvadiva. 
<bibRefCitation pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Crosnier (1975)</bibRefCitation>
examined the syntypes and commented that the two specimens are not conspecific. He noted that the specimen from Kolumadulu Island was almost certainly 
<taxonomicName genus="T." lsidName="T. sexlobata" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" rank="species" species="sexlobata">T. sexlobata</taxonomicName>
Miers, 1886, while the other from Suvadiva Island is the actual 
<taxonomicName genus="T." lsidName="T. macrodonta" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" rank="species" species="macrodonta">T. macrodonta</taxonomicName>
which he treated as a distinct species. 
<bibRefCitation author="Apel, M" journalOrPublisher="Fauna of Arabia" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" pagination="159 - 331" title="Taxonomy and zoogeography of the portunid crabs (Crustacea: Decapoda: Brachyura: Portunidae) of the Arabian Gulf and adjacent waters." volume="17" year="1998">Apel and Spiridonov (1998)</bibRefCitation>
re-examined the type material and selected the second syntype from Suvadiva as the lectotype of 
<taxonomicName genus="T." lsidName="T. macrodonta" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" rank="species" species="macrodonta">T. macrodonta</taxonomicName>
s. str.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="3" pageNumber="4">
The present specimen from India is incomplete and not in good condition, but agrees with the description and figures of 
<taxonomicName genus="T." lsidName="T. macrodonta" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" rank="species" species="macrodonta">T. macrodonta</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation pageId="3" pageNumber="4">Crosnier (1975</bibRefCitation>
: fig. 4c, d) and 
<bibRefCitation author="Apel, M" journalOrPublisher="Fauna of Arabia" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" pagination="159 - 331" title="Taxonomy and zoogeography of the portunid crabs (Crustacea: Decapoda: Brachyura: Portunidae) of the Arabian Gulf and adjacent waters." volume="17" year="1998">Apel and Spiridonov (1998</bibRefCitation>
: fig. 59).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
